[[!meta title="Contact"]]

There are many ways to contact us, depending on what you want
to talk about.

All mailing lists are in English unless specified otherwise.

[[!toc levels=2]]

Public mailing lists
====================

These mailing lists are public: subscription is open to anyone. Don't
send compromising information. Please respect the
[[code of conduct|contribute/working_together/code_of_conduct/]].

<a id="tails-support"></a>

tails-support
-------------

[[tails-support@boum.org|support/tails-support]] is the mailing list
dedicated to Tails user support. Subscribe if you have questions or
if you want to help answering questions from others.

Archives of tails-support: <https://mailman.boum.org/pipermail/tails-support/>.

<form method="POST" action="https://mailman.boum.org/subscribe/tails-support">
	<input class="text" name="email" value=""/>
	<input class="button" type="submit" value="Subscribe"/>
</form>

